{"tid":947593,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"成日都好大汗","createTime":"2018-12-19T11:22:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-06T09:43:17.000Z","uid":35112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0e26a59259126baa0040d10748c340ea86ed43ba","tid":947593,"uid":35112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T11:22:03.000Z","msg":"早上10點幾開始就會出汗，不斷咁出<br />\n差唔多成個鐘先停<br />\n之前3點幾又出<br />\n同埋條腰一著褲，就長期出汗<br />\n搞到個人好唔舒服<br />\n<br />\n同埋冇咩尿痾，好似去晒汗到咁<br />\n<br />\n瞓覺第二朝，個床板會濕咗<br />\n有冇人知可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"874af38ae85e913ef377bd0f0f5f37e316c01c3a","tid":947593,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T11:24:43.000Z","msg":"剪汗線?"},{"pid":"3b96e09f29b78472160506d39a7b3ff029a8a00f","tid":947593,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T11:25:46.000Z","msg":"有冇成日口乾？"},{"pid":"88a3ec475372402a76fe418c64faa5e11d6b7eb4","tid":947593,"uid":35112,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3b96e09f29b78472160506d39a7b3ff029a8a00f","tid":947593,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T11:25:46.000Z","msg":"有冇成日口乾？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T11:32:14.000Z","msg":"有 飲好多水<br />\n但飲完又冇咩尿痾， <br />\n飲得多就好易出汗<br />\n一日痾得5次尿到，早上一次，中午飯一次，放工一次，返到屋企一次，瞓前一次"},{"pid":"fd5549b7782be4f3d99407b7c4208f8bdd2582a4","tid":947593,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T11:36:20.000Z","msg":"腎有事"},{"pid":"09bda946dd1f90c8ac09d9daec941ae937f78a26","tid":947593,"uid":197005,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T11:40:16.000Z","msg":"睇醫生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"327dc75b2f568c4b5188436b18ff0a2a622f9a2e","tid":947593,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco